article:
Developed with astro and scss I present to you a linkbio template with the neumorphism design style for users who feel limited by the free version of Linktree.


This template is perfect for those looking for a customizable, easy-to-use solution to share multiple links through a single link in their social media bio.

Benefits

Customizable: You can easily customize this template to fit your brand and personal style.

Easy to use: This template is easy to use, even if you have no coding experience.

Free: This template is completely free to use.

Support for multiple links: Like Linktree, you can share multiple links through a single link in your social media bio.

No limitations: Unlike the free version of Linktree, this template has no limitations. You have access to all the features without having to pay.
